Description:
fusion-ACT (advanced chiplets technology) offers semiconductor design service (ip/chiplet/sip), and decent design-for-resilient #supplychain strategy.
【Our solutions】
1. top-down / #chiplet design flows facilitate your BOM1->BOM2 migration and optimal system #PPAC (performance, power, formfactor, cost)
2. decent SiP integrations enable #sensorfusion , #reusability , #edgeAIoT and #resilientsupplychain, #PLC (product life cycle), etc.
3.  strategical #PLC (product life cycle) plan, from prototyping / NRE to mass production.
4. design/process #porting , consumer-to- #automotive , design-for-variation, etc ( #memory , #floorplan , 2d-to-3d stack, #thermal , #stress aware ...)
【Our experiences】
#DFM #ecosystem FAE & #referencedesign flows, including:
- statistical #DRC , #dfmscoring,  #patternmatch (PM, #drcplus ) methodologies;
- #dfm modeling: #yield modeling, prediction and gap analysis; #CMP (chemical-mechanical polish) planarization; #lpc (litho process check), #opc (optical proximity check);
- #dfmfixing , #routability , #eco in #digitaldesign flows;
- #edfm calculator in #analogdesign flows, #presim vs. #postsim iterations;
- #thermal #em aware in #powerrail #cowos designs & #3dic calculator;
